{"tid":729992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳海航抵押香港山頂豪宅Twelve Peaks","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T04:53:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62a30404a5aab9bca39c37832fd65c5ce3ea6e43","tid":729992,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530761390_bd0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530761390_bd0f.jpg&h=ead0f480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資金出現問題的海航又抵押資產，根據《南華日報》報道指，海航集團擬將山頂豪宅Twelve Peaks的6號屋抵押貸款，估值約5.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，海航主席陳峰在港會居於Twelve Peaks的6號屋。<br />\n<br />\nTwelve Peaks由新地（016）發展，14年發售時，實用呎價10.9萬元至17.57萬元。8號屋於七一售價價高達7.3億元，實用4,784方呎，呎價約152,592元，買家選用第3號付款辦法，獲15%印花稅回贈，折實成交價6.205億元，呎價約129,703元，呎價創項目新高。"},{"pid":"342b71ee3fa2df4993d9497d568ff1d130284f8d","tid":729992,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"仲未扺押既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}